data.description: Exquisite single story semi-custom home set on 1.03 private acres in an intimate gated community of only 5 homes in the heart of Mandarin! Meticulously designed home showcases designer tilework, LVP, quartz countertops, high-end cabinetry, oversized kitchen island & double walk-in closets in owners suite. Gas stove, gas fireplace, & gas water heater w/ 500 gal underground propane tank. Other deluxe features incl whole home generator, epoxy garage floor, rain water filtration system, large tiled screened lanai, all inside lighting upgraded incl ceiling fans, fenced backyard w/ 8 ft vinyl fencing incl RV gate for RV/boat storage, & irrigation well (no cost for water). Guest room has a built-in 3 person infrared sauna. This home is a must see! 1st Mortgage is Assumable at 2.75% for VA Buyers
